    <div class="infobox-row"><div class="infobox-label">Education</div><div class="infobox-data"><a href="https://itp.nyu.edu">NYU ITP</a> (MPS, 2026)<br/><a href="https://nyu.edu">NYU</a> (BA, 2024)</div></div>
